title: China state visit diary: No surprises for President Xi at leaders’ press conference
text: The two leaders took only two questions at their press conference. The BBC’s Laura Kuenssberg managed an intricate query that took in the closure of steel works, the carriage in which Mr Xi was conveyed to Buckingham Palace, and civil rights in China. Read more
